                  <a href="/feed.xml" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" id="rss-icon"><img src="https://cdn.glitch.global/c4e475b2-a54e-47e0-973c-ed0bd1b46262/rss.svg?v=1669925974414" alt="RSS" /></a>
